Create Logo & Title 9

STEP 1: Download the images needed to create this step from the  


above. 


STEP 2: Create the US Custom Logo. Click Insert inside the top toolbar, select image, find the US Custom logo and select. 


STEP 3: Format size and location of US Custom Logo. The image displays what should be in the General tab.


STEP 4: Create the Title for our dashboard. Click Insert then text box, select the font size as 28 then center the alignment, next you will format the size and location of the text box, finally format the background. 


All steps are shown in the GIF below.
